  "Description": {
    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-technology\">Personal Surface Radar</span> augmentation for the Multi-Tool. <br><br>The Scanner releases a high-energy pulse that reveals any <span class=\"name name-commodity\">critical survival resources</span> in the immediate area. Data is transmitted via the Exosuit directly into the user's visual nervous system.<br> <br>Press <span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span> to activate a local scan.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "用于多用途工具的<span class=\"name name-technology\">个人地标雷达</span>增强设备。<br><br>扫描仪可以发射出高能脉冲，显示附近地区任意<span class=\"name name-commodity\">重要的生存资源</span>。数据将通过套装直接传回使用者的视觉神经系统。<br> <br>按下<span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span>开始本地扫描。",
    "TencentChinese": "用于多用途工具的<span class=\"name name-technology\">个人地标雷达</span>增强设备。<br><br>扫描仪可以发射出高能脉冲，显示附近地区任意<span class=\"name name-commodity\">重要的生存资源</span>。数据将通过套装直接传回使用者的视觉神经系统。<br> <br>按下<span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span>开始本地扫描。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "工具組的<span class=\"name name-technology\">個人用地表雷達</span>擴充元件。<br><br>掃描器能釋放高能量脈衝，找出當前區域的任何<span class=\"name name-commodity\">關鍵維生資源</span>。資料會經由強化套裝，直接傳送至使用者的視覺神經系統。<br><br>按 <span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span> 啟動當地掃描。"
  },
